This repository contains a Raspberry Pi/Linux C++ port derived from the
Adafruit SHT4X library. The original upstream notice is preserved below
verbatim in support of the upstream redistribution notice.

Original upstream notice from `Adafruit_SHT4x.h`:

/*!
 *  @file Adafruit_SHT4x.h
 *
 *  This is a library for the SHT4x Digital Humidity & Temp Sensor
 *
 *  Designed specifically to work with the SHT4x Humidity & Temp Sensor
 *  -----> https://www.adafruit.com/product/4885
 *
 *  These sensors use I2C to communicate, 2 pins are required to interface
